58% in one cohort and 49% in the other

726
00:43:46.416 --> 00:43:47.696
cohort that were still alive.

727
00:43:49.316 --> 00:43:53.016
Could you just comment some regarding that on the median follow-up, because you've

728
00:43:53.056 --> 00:43:55.496
mentioned a good median follow-up, but we didn't see it.

729
00:43:55.956 --> 00:43:57.736
What is the median follow-up in each cohort?

730
00:43:57.816 --> 00:44:00.536
Because you know it's a very classical bias of that kind of

731
00:44:00.576 --> 00:44:04.536
comparisons that the chemo group may

732
00:44:04.636 --> 00:44:08.336
have a much longer-term median follow-up as compared

733
00:44:08.346 --> 00:44:12.336
to the T-DXd, and it might have an impact on the way you'll be

734
