827
00:48:55.956 --> 00:48:59.946
So just to give a little bit of a background, we know that hypertension is

828
00:48:59.976 --> 00:49:03.906
a major public health burden. There's a high prevalence, and we see an increased

829
00:49:03.956 --> 00:49:05.216
prevalence also among

830
00:49:07.236 --> 00:49:10.596
the younger population, leading to a longer

831
00:49:10.636 --> 00:49:14.036
exposure of antihypertensive drugs among this

832
00:49:14.056 --> 00:49:17.576
population. And so there is an increased interest in identifying the

833
00:49:17.616 --> 00:49:20.656
long-term effects of these medications on the general

834
00:49:20.696 --> 00:49:24.336
population. ARBs and ACE are first-line

835
00:49:24.396 --> 00:49:27.475
therapies, and they're really clinically interchangeably used.

836
00:49:27.536 --> 00:49:31.496
They're both effective for cardiovascular disease prevention.

837
00:49:32.196 --> 00:49:36.016
They're currently prescribed among over 40 million

838
00:49:36.236 --> 00:49:40.156
US adults. On the right side, you can see they both act on

839
00:49:40.196 --> 00:49:43.076
the renin-angiotensin system, the R**S system.

840
00:49:44.516 --> 00:49:45.756
ACE acts higher up,

841
00:49:47.096 --> 00:49:50.776
inhibiting the transformation from angiotensin 1 to angiotensin 2,

842
00:49:51.776 --> 00:49:55.296
while also leading to an increase in accumulation of

843
00:49:55.316 --> 00:49:58.696
bradykinin. An ARB, on the other hand, acts much lower in

844
00:49:58.796 --> 00:50:02.676
the signaling pathway, inhibiting the

845
00:50:02.796 --> 00:50:06.596
AT1 receptor, but really leaving the AT2 receptor signaling

846
00:50:06.616 --> 00:50:06.936
alone.

847
00:50:08.176 --> 00:50:09.676
So what is currently known about

848
00:50:10.596 --> 00:50:13.796
the risk of cancer with these medications?

849
00:50:14.476 --> 00:50:17.376
Overall, the evidence is inconclusive.

850
00:50:18.016 --> 00:50:21.236
Most of the studies have been done more in stromal cancers, including lung,

851
00:50:21.956 --> 00:50:23.676
