00:53:30.516 --> 00:53:34.176
On the right side, just some statistics of our study population.

903
00:53:34.236 --> 00:53:37.646
There were 2.6 million US veterans included in this

904
00:53:37.736 --> 00:53:40.676
study. Mean age was about 63 years.

905
00:53:41.196 --> 00:53:45.116
We had 10% ARB initiators and 90%

906
00:53:45.176 --> 00:53:49.056
