916
00:54:20.216 --> 00:54:24.196
On the right side, you see the cumulative incidence curves, the dotted

917
00:54:24.236 --> 00:54:26.516
lines indicating the diagnosis-free deaths.

918
00:54:26.576 --> 00:54:29.576
As a reminder, that was where cancer was the competing event.

919
00:54:29.596 --> 00:54:30.696
And incidence cancer

920
00:54:31.576 --> 00:54:35.116
diagnosis in the solid lines. Red indicating ACE

921
00:54:35.156 --> 00:54:36.076
and ARB

922
00:54:37.096 --> 00:54:38.316
in blue.

923
00:54:39.156 --> 00:54:42.636
In relative comparisons, we observed a 20% to 25% lower risk.

924
00:54:43.116 --> 00:54:45.736
At the same time, we did not observe any

925
00:54:47.096 --> 00:54:50.504
major differences in diagnosis-free mortality reallyNot

926
00:54:50.524 --> 00:54:54.464
indicating a early excess risk of death in

927
00:54:54.504 --> 00:54:55.224
