934
00:55:21.424 --> 00:55:24.544
Here is just a snapshot of the results at the 10-year time point.

935
00:55:24.984 --> 00:55:28.844
And you can clearly see over the age of 70, where we observed a 30% decreased

936
00:55:28.924 --> 00:55:29.184
