2048
01:58:25.174 --> 01:58:28.934
and pre-registration of study protocols prior to

2049
01:58:28.974 --> 01:58:32.794
initiation and analysis. The FDA's Advancing

2050
01:58:32.894 --> 01:58:36.794
Real World Evidence program has established new regulatory pathways, and

2051
01:58:36.854 --> 01:58:40.814
